{"id":152760,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/上海实施一户一犬政策/","date":"2011-05-17T04:00:36Z","modified":"2011-05-17T04:00:36Z","title":"上海实施一户一犬政策","content":"<p>仿佛是令人回想起1976年开始的独生子女政策，上海宣布引入了一户一犬政策。上海大约有80万只狗，其中只有1.4万只狗登记过，超过60万狗未登记。 《上海市养犬管理条例》从15日开始正式实施，每户家庭限养一条狗。《条例》规定，犬龄满3个月的犬只必须要接受狂犬病强制免疫；养犬人应当具有完全民事行为能力，在本市有固定的居住场所，并实行“一户一犬”原则，也就是一套住房限养一只犬；单位养犬的，应当在办公楼、居民小区以外设有专门的圈养设施，配备看管人员；禁养獒犬、狼犬和斗牛犬三类犬种，藏獒、斗牛獒犬、法国狼犬、德国牧羊犬、牛头梗、杜宾犬等知名犬类私人均不得饲养。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14e14729/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E4%B8%80%E6%88%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%8A%AC%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F16%2F1111230%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E4%B8%80%E6%88%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%8A%AC%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F16%2F1111230%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092485018/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14e14729/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092485018/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14e14729/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=nG1LLZ2OVgE:_paM1Fmw650:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=nG1LLZ2OVgE:_paM1Fmw650:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POS